== Research Interests
My research aims to develop *reliable*, *explainable*, and *practical* decision-making algorithms. I am also interested in methods with elegant mathematical modeling.
Currently, my focus is on enhancing the *reasoning capabilities* of large language models.
- Algorithms (Algorithmic Game Theory, Online Learning Theory, Ad Auction)
- Machine Learning (Explainable AI, Edge computing, Recommendation system)
- Large Language Models (Long Context, Enhanced Reasoning, Efficient Training)

